- cargo new rust-chat (remove src and create workspace)

- cargo new backend

- cargo new frontend

- cargo new common --lib

- add rocket to backend

- cargo run --bin backend

- take info from rocket ws website

- add ChatRoom in backend

- in browser (inspection) add in console (ws = new WebSocket('ws://127.0.0.1:8000'))

- cargo install trunk

- rustup target add wasm32-unknown-unknown

- cd frontend

- trunk serve

- add index.html